Its natural habitats are subtropical or tropical moist shrubland, rivers, and freshwater lakes.', descrizione_fonte = 'Wikipedia (en)', descrizione_url = 'https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ladder-tailed_nightjar' where nome_scientifico = 'Hydropsalis climacocerca' and descrizione is null;
